description: The Gymnast is coming off a crushing defeat by Isis, and is looking to rebound from that with a victory. With 4 matches under her belt she feels confidant that she can defeat The Trouper, who has 6 losses in 10 matches. The Trouper is just that, a fighter, who has slowly caught on to how US works. She hopes to use her experience against a younger, stronger, faster opponent.
title: The Gymnast (1-3)
